data.description: Acreage close to all the amenities! This once-beautiful brick home needs a lot of help but will make a beautiful home for the next owner. Hardwood floors, beautiful woodwork throughout. Living room and dining room have beautiful built-ins with glass fronts, hardwood floors need finished, walls and ceilings need repair. Three bedrooms and bathroom upstairs with a rear enclosed porch off the upstairs bathroom. With over 2 acres you have plenty of space to add a garage if you choose and so much more. Loads of potential and possibility. Cash only as home does not have a functioning kitchen currently. Newer septic, well pump, and roof.
